本能的に突破口も
Instinctively, even the breakthrough

25
00:07:57,308 --> 00:07:59,608
堂々巡りの走馬灯
Is a revolving lantern of circular logic

26
00:07:59,908 --> 00:08:02,608
迷宮に囚り込まれてゆくわ
Getting lured into the labyrinth

27
00:08:02,608 --> 00:08:05,108
革命的に飾れ
Adorn it revolutionarily

28
00:08:05,508 --> 00:08:08,508
不条理めく見学ツアー
The absurd observation tour

29
00:08:08,508 --> 00:08:11,508
どわっはっはと愛を注入
Injecting love with a big 'Dwahaha!'

30
